lead_paragraph: First time Olympic winners, including Australian teen Kyle Chalmers in the 100 meters freestyle, plundered three of the four golds in the Rio pool on Wednesday but there was no getting past Katie Ledecky.

headline.main: Swimming: Night of Individual Firsts in Rio Pool
